WEBVTT

00:12:29.119 --> 00:12:33.684
Just a few weeks after Suzanne's visit
to her brother and his new wife,

00:12:34.237 --> 00:12:35.514
their neighbor,

00:12:36.732 --> 00:12:38.873
Craig Stephen Hicks,

00:12:38.897 --> 00:12:40.642
murdered them,

00:12:40.666 --> 00:12:45.447
as well as Yusor's sister, Razan,
who was visiting for the afternoon,

00:12:45.471 --> 00:12:47.230
in their apartment,

00:12:47.754 --> 00:12:49.509
execution style,

00:12:49.533 --> 00:12:53.489
after posting anti-Muslim statements
on his Facebook page.

00:12:54.058 --> 00:12:55.802
He shot Deah eight times.

00:12:57.254 --> 00:13:01.289
So bigotry isn't just immoral,
it can even be lethal.